description.plain: Harry Michael, better known as Masked Wolf, is a rapper hailing from Sydney, Australia. He started posting songs on YouTube and SoundCloud in 2018, but achieved an unexpected breakthrough in 2021 when his song “Astronaut in the Ocean” went viral on TikTok.
